"children":"When the AR aging report comes out three weeks after the period ends, the optimal window to act on the findings in that report has already passed. Reporting cadence that does not match decision timelines produces insight that is always about the past, never about the present."}]]}]]}]]}]]}]}],"$undefined",["$","section",null,{"className":"block block--ink","id":"solution","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"block-head fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"eyebrow","children":"The solution"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"display display--light","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"Reporting that gives leadership clarity. <em>Analytics that produce action.</em>"}}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Hired Billing Support pulls data from your billing, AR, denial, operational, and patient engagement systems — synthesizes it into structured reports with clear interpretation and specific recommended actions — and delivers it to leadership on a schedule that allows real decisions, not retrospective observations."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"two-col fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-list","children":[["$","div","01",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"01"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"Multi-source data synthesis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Billing software, EHR, clearinghouse, AR reports, denial queues, and operational metrics pulled together and synthesized into a single coherent view of practice performance — so leadership sees the full picture, not disconnected fragments."}]]}]]}],["$","div","02",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"02"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"KPI tracking and trend analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Collection rate, denial rate, days in AR, clean claim rate, AR agi